            -> [T-44 (Object 136) - Soviet medium tank, developed in 1943-1944 by the design bureau of Uralvagonzavod under the leadership of A. A. Morozov, was intended to replace the T-34 in the role of the main and medium tank of the Red Army Armed Forces of the USSR.](*<- lang_en;;*);;
